item.description: About Me Link to heading You can find my CV here (Updated 10/28/22). Hello, my name is James Oswald! I am PhD student at Rensselaer Polytechnic Institute and graduate researcher with the The Rensselaer Artificial Intelligence and Reasoning (RAIR) Laboratory, under Professor Selmer Bringsjord. My primary research interest is in Artificial Intelligence (AI), particularly Artificial General Intelligence (AGI), that is, how we can best create single AI agents that performs well on general tasks.
